  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <div xml:id="Aink41-kilavi">
        <p type="edition">kaḻaṟit teruṭṭaṟ pālarākiya akampukal marapiṉ vāyilkaḷ pukuntuḻit
          talaivaṉaiyum pāṇaṉ mutalākiya pakkattāraiyum ikaḻntu talaivi kūṟiyatu.</p>
        <p type="translation" xml:lang="en"> </p>
      </div>

      <div xml:id="Aink41">
        <lg type="edition">
          <l> taṉpārpput tiṉṉu maṉpiṉ mutalaiyoṭu</l>
          <l>veṇpūm poykait tavaṉū reṉpa ataṉāṟ</l>
          <l>ṟaṉco luṇarntōr mēṉi</l>
          <l>poṉpōṟ ceyyu mūrkiḻa vōṉē.</l>
        </lg>
        <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
          <l>They say his village has ponds with white flowers [in them]</l>
          <l>and heartless crocodiles that eat their [own] young. Because of that</l>
          <l>the lord of the village turns </l>
          <l>the bodies of those who heard his words</l>
          <l>[pale] as gold.</l>


        </lg>
      </div>
    </body>
